{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "de4c6e5b-6a1b-44d4-b4ea-0f4f5df8f003",
    "name": "Dllni - Cleaning Worker Module",
    "description": "## Base URL and Prefix\n- Collection variable `{{baseUrl}}` defaults to `http://Dllni.test`.\n- Prefix: `/api/v1`.\n\n## Authentication\n- All endpoints here require Sanctum token.\n- Header: `Authorization: Bearer {{token}}`.\n\n## Worker Scope\n- Most endpoints require an authenticated user with linked worker profile (`user.worker`).\n- If no worker exists, API may return `403`.\n\n## Props Format\n- Pagination: `perPage`, `page`.\n- Filters: `filter[field]=value` (AND semantics).\n- Validation errors: `{ \"message\": string, \"errors\": { \"field\": [string] } }`.\n\n## Common Status Values\n- booking statuses often include: `pending`, `worker_assigned`, `in_progress`, `completed`, `cancelled`.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://Dllni.test"
    },
    {
      "key": "token",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "bookingId",
      "value": "1"
    },
    {
      "key": "warningId",
      "value": "1"
    }
  ],
