            "description": "Paginated worker bookings list.\n\nUseful filters:\n- filter[forCurrentWorker]=1\n- filter[status]=pending|in_progress|completed|cancelled\n- filter[hasDispute]=1\n- filter[scheduledDate]=YYYY-MM-DD"
