            "description": "No body required.\n\nIf booking pricing is provisional (`isPricingFinal=false`), acceptance finalizes pricing using worker home location and customer coordinates.\n\nReturns updated booking resource including:\n- `travelDistanceKm`\n- `adminMargin`\n- `isPricingFinal`\n- finalized `totalPrice`"
          },
